name: qt5_base
deps: openssl, xorg_libraries, libjpg_turbo, icu, fontconfig, dbus, make_ca, libmng, libpng, libtiffi, libxkbcommon, mesa, mtdev, pcre, sqlite, wayland, xcb_util_image, xcb_util_keysyms, xcb_util_renderutil, xcb_util, qm, libinput, pciutils
desc:
Qt5 is a cross-platform application framework that is widely used 
for developing application software with a graphical user interface 
(GUI) (in which cases Qt5 is classified as a widget toolkit), and also 
used for developing non-GUI programs such as command-line tools and consoles for servers.
